{"tid":1759693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國拉美國人 華裔女子被中國拘留","createTime":"2019-11-27T21:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T18:14:22.000Z","uid":165683,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4143f2c5bbaac7ebfa5a584900a559c90775ea99","tid":1759693,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T21:10:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-woman-languishing-in-china-jail-families-worry-20191127/5183249.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fus-woman-languishing-in-china-jail-families-worry-20191127%2F5183249.html&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DYRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=2bb9bf8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-woman-languishing-in-china-jail-families-worry-20191127/5183249.html</a><br />\n<br />\n亞利桑那州一名華裔女子目前已被中國拘留近三個多月，她的親戚朋友愈來愈擔心她的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n江世萍來自亞利桑那州噴泉山，是當地一家按摩店的老闆。她和兒子江大衛今年8月飛往中國參加她父親的葬禮，航班29日剛抵達上海時，江世萍就被拘留了。<br />\n<br />\n江大衛告訴全國廣播公司新聞頻道（NBC News），有人登上了飛機，帶走了他的母親，並在沒有任何解釋的情況下拘留了她。 &ldquo;我媽媽出示了美國護照，他們拿走了她的手機，我媽媽問為甚麼要帶走她，他們說以後會告訴她。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"3fe3c8cd6a0b15171679b231bcd0a51c1032a11e","tid":1759693,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T21:11:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cda1aaf032672bfe0336fa3668816cec28802dc5","tid":1759693,"uid":163404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T21:11:36.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af601fa4ef9a80736295b49d02ad563814cc48e2","tid":1759693,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T21:13:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1d26d0746c5f7614e216b6e21a0abd349f2bc212","tid":1759693,"uid":122601,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T21:14:25.000Z","msg":"姐係移民蝗啦"},{"pid":"ee2aeb2681f9fd541d35530b1328dce7ca88342e","tid":1759693,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy